        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Alice Green",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev001",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "My daily stop. The baristas know my name and my order. Consistently excellent espresso and the rotating single-origin pour-overs are a treat. Capitol Hill needed exactly this.",
        "createTime": "2026-02-05T07:45:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-02-05T07:45:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Alice, you're part of our morning routine too! ☕ See you tomorrow!",
          "updateTime": "2026-02-05T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev002",
        "reviewId": "rev002",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Brian Chen",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev002",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FOUR",
        "comment": "Great coffee and nice neighborhood vibe. Gets busy post-9am but lines move fast. The oat milk latte is consistently good — hard to do well and they nail it.",
        "createTime": "2026-02-20T08:30:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-02-20T08:30:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev003",
        "reviewId": "rev003",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Claire Ross",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev003",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "Best cold brew in Seattle. The concentration is perfect — most places over-dilute. Grabbed their seasonal lavender latte too and it's become my new weekend obsession.",
        "createTime": "2026-03-10T10:30:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-03-10T10:30:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Claire, cold brew concentration is something we obsess over — glad it shows! The lavender latte comes back every spring. 🌸",
          "updateTime": "2026-03-10T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev004",
        "reviewId": "rev004",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Dan Park",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev004",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "THREE",
        "comment": "Coffee is good but the music is way too loud for a coffee shop. Hard to have a conversation or concentrate. Dialed up past the point that makes sense for the space.",
        "createTime": "2026-03-25T14:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-03-25T14:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev005",
        "reviewId": "rev005",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Elena Russo",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev005",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FOUR",
        "comment": "Working remotely from here has become a habit. Good wifi, plenty of outlets, and the staff never rush you. The cortado is exceptional.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-08T10:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-08T10:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev006",
        "reviewId": "rev006",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Felix Torres",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev006",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "Brought my daughter who's learning about coffee culture. The barista spent 10 minutes explaining the difference between processing methods and let her smell the green beans. Educational and delightful.",
        "createTime": "2026-04-20T11:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-04-20T11:00:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Felix, we love sharing the journey from seed to cup! Sounds like a future barista in the making. 🌱",
          "updateTime": "2026-04-20T23:59:00Z"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev007",
        "reviewId": "rev007",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Gina Adams",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev007",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FOUR",
        "comment": "The pastry selection rivals specialty bakeries. The almond croissant is absolutely buttery and worth the calories. Combined with a flat white — perfect Seattle morning.",
        "createTime": "2026-05-15T08:00:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-05-15T08:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "name": "accounts/100000001/locations/200000001/reviews/rev008",
        "reviewId": "rev008",
        "reviewer": {
          "displayName": "Harry Kim",
          "profilePhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/mock_rev008",
          "isAnonymous": false
        },
        "starRating": "FIVE",
        "comment": "Visited for the first time while apartment hunting in the neighbourhood and now I want to move to Capitol Hill specifically to be close to this coffee shop. That's how good it is.",
        "createTime": "2026-06-01T09:30:00Z",
        "updateTime": "2026-06-01T09:30:00Z",
        "reviewReply": {
          "comment": "Harry, we take full responsibility for any apartment decisions that bring you to Capitol Hill! The neighbourhood is worth it. 😄",
          "updateTime": "2026-06-01T23:59:00Z"
        }
      }
